   PEGASUS GOLD Inc. (Spokane, Wash.) -- William G. Wilson,
54 years old, executive vice president and chief financial
officer of Nova Corp., has been named to the board of this
mining company. He succeeds Stanton B. Bennet, who retired
last December.
